<div class="title">Quite Synergistic Subcutaneous Experiment</div>
<div class="substance">2C-I (SC) & 1,4 Butanediol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Mr.+Hazlitt&Exact=1">Mr. Hazlitt</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Mr. Hazlitt. "Quite Synergistic Subcutaneous Experiment: An Experience with 2C-I (SC) & 1,4 Butanediol (exp9417)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 13, 2001. erowid.org/exp/9417</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
